# 默认忽略所有
*

# 只跟踪以下目录和文件
!.claude-plugin/
!.claude-plugin/**
!cli/
!cli/**
!mcp/
!mcp/**
!extension/
!extension/**
!skills/
!skills/**

# 仅跟踪稳定的公开用户文档与 SEO 资料；内部设计、计划和草稿保持忽略
!docs/
!docs/agent-tool.md
!docs/share-codex-chat.md
!docs/share-claude-code-chat.md
!docs/directory-submission-kit.md
!examples/
!examples/hello-previewship/
